Stock - Class in cscd210Classes
A basic Stock class with a ticker symbol, company name, purchase price and current price.
Stock() - Constructor for class cscd210Classes.Stock
The Default Value Constructor -- sets the company name to DOW Jones Industrial Average, the symbol to DOW and the current price to 12.
Stock(String, String, double) - Constructor for class cscd210Classes.Stock
The Explicit Value Constructor -- sets the company name to the value passed in, the symbol to the passed in value, and the current price to the passed in current price.
Stock(String, double, String) - Constructor for class cscd210Classes.Stock
The Explicit Value Constructor -- Must call the constuctor that is passed in this order (ticker, companyName, and currentPrice) The purchase price is set to 5
